      "youtube_chapter": "Iron Man HUD",
      "act": 2,
      "act_title": "Reject: no exact coords",
      "on_screen": "azimuth \u2260 position",
      "narration": "First problem: Vision Pro gives direction from the mic, not an exact coordinate. The pin is guesswork \u2014 it drifts and feels wrong.",
