      "act_title": "Reject: off-screen hazard",
      "on_screen": "Off-screen = hazard",
      "narration": "Second \u2014 for accessibility \u2014 an urgent sound behind you might never enter your field of view. A baby crying pinned outside your gaze is a missed alert.",
