      "act_title": "Iron Man HUD pivot",
      "on_screen": "Iron Man HUD",
      "narration": "So we pivoted to an Iron Man\u2013style HUD \u2014 captions and sound labels on a panel that stays in view. Head-relative, not world-hunted. That's what the demo shows.",
